reviews.text: Always with long queue during lunch here! It’s holidays today and took a chance to drop in after sometimes ago. Japanese restaurant are generally not disappointed. The food are always up to their standard. Their place is always clean and tidying as well as nicely decorated.
Not cheap but delicious food with good atmosphere
Too chain store feel. Quality cannot keep up with the original Japanese branch
Ramen in black garlic oil + shrimp tampura recommended.
Fantastic Japanese foods in a reasonable price which brings u beyond expectation!

reviews.text: Always with long queue during lunch here! It’s holidays today and took a chance to drop in after sometimes ago. Japanese restaurant are generally not disappointed. The food are always up to their standard. Their place is always clean and tidying as well as nicely decorated.
這裡的拉麵的湯底和拉麵的口感都不錯，有很多肉，肉的味道很好。最特別是可以要求加生蒜和辣粉，職員會給你工具，讓你自製生蒜蓉，很適合嗜辣和吃生蒜的人。
職員比較冷淡和沒甚麼禮貌，食物一般！
Not cheap but delicious food with good atmosphere
Too chain store feel. Quality cannot keep up with the original Japanese branch
